articles.title: Caitlin Clark Turns Heads With Postgame Celebration On Tuesday - Yahoo Sports
articles.description: Caitlin Clark secured the first piece of hardware of her pro basketball career yesterday as the Indiana Fever won the Commissioner's Cup title in a win over the Minnesota Lynx.
